@{
    ViewBag.Title = "Help";
}
@Scripts.Render("~/bundles/jquery")
<h2>Help</h2>
<div class="row">
    <div class="col-md-8">
        <h3>About File Repository</h3>
        <p>
            This website supports the storage, retrieval, and viewing of source code
            files. A user will be able to upload a file or folder, view any of the files in a folder, specify dependency information,
            and retrieve a selected file and all its dependencies, all from a browser. The web service supports synchronizing the
            contents of a server folder with a specified folder on the client machine.
        </p>
        <p>
            It supports:
        </p>
        <ul>

            <li>Uploading a specified client file to a selected folder on the server.</li>
            <li>
                Creating new folders on the server.
            </li>
            <li>
                Specifying persistent dependency relationships between files selected by name and date.
            </li>
            <li>
                Viewing a selected file’s text.
            </li>
            <li>
                Downloading a selected file and optionally all its dependencies.
            </li>
        </ul>
    </div>
    <div class="col-md-4">
        <h3>About the Roles</h3>
        <p>In this websites, there are 3 roles:</p>
        <ul>
            <li>
                <strong>Normal Users:</strong> Just view and download the files in the server.
            </li>
            <li>
                <strong>Developers:</strong> Upload files; Create directories and specify files dependencies.
            </li>
            <li>
                <strong>Administrator:</strong> Manage Roles; Rename Directories'; Delete files.
            </li>
        </ul>

    </div>
</div>